# 10 Segment LED Bar Graph (SKU:FIT0188)

<div id="siteSub">From DFRobot Electronic Product Wiki and Tutorial: Arduino and Robot Wiki-DFRobot.com</div>

<div id="jump-to-nav" class="mw-jump">Jump to:[navigation](#mw-navigation), [search](#p-search)</div>

</div>

<div id="bodyContent">

<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">

<div class="thumb tright">

<div class="thumbinner" style="width:202px;">[![](/wiki/images/thumb/4/4f/10LEDBarGraph.jpg/200px-10LEDBarGraph.jpg)](https://www.dfrobot.com/product-636.html)

<div class="thumbcaption">

<div class="magnify">[](/wiki/index.php/File:10LEDBarGraph.jpg "Enlarge")</div>

[10 Segment LED Bar Graph](https://www.dfrobot.com/product-636.html)</div>

</div>

</div>

